sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant Unity as Unity Client
    participant API as Backend API
    participant Photon as Photon Fusion Cloud

    Note over U, U: User Launches Unity App

    U->>Unity: Login (Username/Password)
    Unity->>API: POST /auth/login
    API-->>Unity: Return JWT Token

    U->>Unity: Select Room to Join
    Unity->>API: GET /rooms/{id} (Check Access)
    API-->>Unity: Return Room Details (inc. UUID)
    
    Note over Unity, Photon: CRITICAL: Using Room UUID as Session Name

    Unity->>Photon: Start(SessionName = Room.UUID)
    activate Photon
    Photon->>Photon: Create or Join Session
    Photon-->>Unity: Connected (Player Spawned)
    deactivate Photon

    Unity->>API: GET /assets (Fetch Room Content)
    API-->>Unity: Return Asset URLs
    Unity->>Unity: Spawn 3D Models (Runtime)
    
    Note over U, Path: User can now see others & interact
